10 AS INTRODUCED
11 A Resolution raising awareness for organ donation;
recognizing the month of April 2026 as National
12 Donate Life Month.
13
14
15
16 WHEREAS, one of the most meaningful gifts that a human being can
17 bestow upon another is the gift of life. In the last 30 years,
18 Donate Life America and the Donate Life Community have registered
19 170 million organ, eye, and tissue donors in the United States; and
20 WHEREAS, over 100,000 men, women, and children are currently on
21 the national waiting list for organ transplantation; and
22 WHEREAS, every 8 minutes another person is added to the waiting
23 list; and
24
